description:
Sierra Ferrell performs "Fox Hunt" live in studio
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube

During a tour stop in the Twin Cities to play a show at First Avenue in Minneapolis, Sierra Ferrell and her band visited The Current for a studio session hosted by Jessica Paxton. Watch and listen to a performance of "Fox Hunt" above.

Musicians
Sierra Ferrell – vocals, fiddle, guitar
Joshua Rilko – mandolin, guitar, backing vocals
Geoffrey Saunders – bass, backing vocals
Oliver Bates Craven – guitars, fiddle, backing vocals
Matty Meyer – drums

Credits
Guest – @SierraFerrell

Producer – Derrick Stevens
